    p This is Chessmate, the world best ever chess tournament application. Enjoy!
    p This is version 1.0.0. Have a look at the 
        a(href="documentation.txt",target="_blank") documentation
        |  to know what this release contains and how to use the app.

    hr
    p Players 
        //button#loadit.btn.btn-sm.btn-light Load from memory
    ul.nav.nav-tabs
